                <h1>Ranking the Best Stand-Up Arcade Games of the &#039;80s and &#039;90s</h1>
                <p>
                    <span class="pq-text">Was Tempest better than Dig Dug?</span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</a>
                    </div>
